sentences.english: He is buried in Rochester, New York.
sentences.chinese: 他被埋在紐約的羅切斯特市。

sentences.english: Mr Rochester called me closer to the fire.
sentences.chinese: 羅切斯特先生讓我離火近些。

sentences.english: He bought a house in Rochester in his later life.
sentences.chinese: 晚年，他在羅切斯特買了一所房子。

sentences.english: Right. Revd Rochester will officiate at the wedding.
sentences.chinese: 是的，羅切斯特牧師將主持婚禮。

sentences.english: Mr. Rochester wants you to bring Adele to the party.
sentences.chinese: 羅切斯特先生想你帶阿戴列去晚會。

sentences.english: The "Rocheste Royal Cadets" update will be released on March 23.
sentences.chinese: “羅切斯特少年團”將會在3月23日更新。

sentences.english: ESTHER CONWELL: "I was a graduate student at the University of Rochester."
sentences.chinese: 我是羅切斯特大學的一名研究生。

sentences.english: After Jane finds out Mr. Rochester has an insane wife.
sentences.chinese: 簡發現羅切斯特先生有個精神失常的妻子之後。
